253
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:28,664
Admiral-- [clearing throat]
Admiral Scurvy!

254
00:12:28,747 --> 00:12:29,665
My old friend.

255
00:12:30,207 --> 00:12:33,711
It's just like you to, uh, take over
someone else's jovial prank.

256
00:12:34,211 --> 00:12:35,880
Isn't it fun being friends?

257
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:37,423
[singing]

258
00:12:37,506 --> 00:12:38,924
[Scurvy] Absolutely not.

259
00:12:40,384 --> 00:12:41,719
Friends? Heh.

260
00:12:41,802 --> 00:12:42,887
We were friends.

261
00:12:43,179 --> 00:12:46,015
But I've had to rebuild
my last three ships

262
00:12:46,098 --> 00:12:48,142
because you set them on fire.

263
00:12:48,434 --> 00:12:50,853
Honestly, who does that?

264
00:12:54,356 --> 00:12:55,357
[shouts]

265
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:02,448
