can you put that aside
for the sake of your friendship?

271
00:13:21,383 --> 00:13:22,676
[all laughing]

272
00:13:24,678 --> 00:13:25,513
Friendship?

273
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:26,514
Oh, boy.

274
00:13:26,931 --> 00:13:30,476
Listen up, kid, friendship is overrated.

275
00:13:30,976 --> 00:13:34,021
There's only one thing in this world
that matters.

276
00:13:34,438 --> 00:13:35,272
Money.

277
00:13:35,439 --> 00:13:36,732
And lucky for you,

278
