As promised.

318
00:15:43,943 --> 00:15:45,778
Scurvy, don't do this.

319
00:15:46,236 --> 00:15:49,156
You and I lived by a sacred code.

320
00:15:49,531 --> 00:15:50,866
The law of the sea.

321
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:52,910
We are like brothers.

322
00:15:53,410 --> 00:15:56,372
If our friendship ever meant anything
to you...

323
00:15:56,455 --> 00:15:57,289
It didn't.

324
00:15:57,748 --> 00:15:59,291
[Sea Hawk grunts]

325
