Uh--

326
00:16:03,754 --> 00:16:04,755
[grunts]

327
00:16:05,589 --> 00:16:07,216
Your friends aren't coming, kid.

328
00:16:07,299 --> 00:16:10,260
I don't think they've even noticed
you're gone.

329
00:16:10,552 --> 00:16:11,637
[laughing]

330
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,515
Oh, friends.

331
00:16:15,808 --> 00:16:18,018
