343
00:16:44,211 --> 00:16:46,714
She-Ra was supposed to save us.

344
00:16:46,797 --> 00:16:50,384
But the Rebellion's in a worse place
than ever since you showed up!

345
00:16:50,467 --> 00:16:53,554
I'm trying my best.
Why can't you see that?

346
00:16:53,637 --> 00:16:56,390
Well, maybe your best isn't good enough!

347
00:16:56,473 --> 00:16:58,892
If it was, my mother would still be here!

348
00:16:59,977 --> 00:17:00,853
