357
00:17:24,626 --> 00:17:26,086
[chuckles] Oh, this?

358
00:17:26,295 --> 00:17:28,964
Catra scratched it out when she was 6.

359
00:17:29,339 --> 00:17:30,466
And now...

360
00:17:30,549 --> 00:17:35,804
