to all of you!

361
00:17:35,888 --> 00:17:37,473
I don't care.

362
00:17:37,556 --> 00:17:39,516
Hey! I'm threatening you!

363
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:40,601
I don't care!

364
00:17:41,769 --> 00:17:42,770
You know what?

365
00:17:42,895 --> 00:17:46,440
It's not easy being the friendly
and upbeat guy all the time.

366
00:17:46,607 --> 00:17:48,984
And I get that it's hard
being friends sometimes.

367
00:17:49,234 --> 00:17:50,486
You gotta work at it.

368
00:17:51,987 --> 00:17:55,741
So, why am I always the only one
who's willing to work at it?

369
00:17:56,116 --> 00:17:59,078
I mean, they didn't even notice I'm gone.

370
00:18:00,496 --> 00:18:02,790
Do whatever you want. I don't care.

371
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:05,542
It's terrible being friends with friends.

372
00:18:05,626 --> 00:18:06,877
[scoffs] Yeesh.

373
00:18:07,419 --> 00:18:09,546
-Ready at the rendezvous point.
-[radio static]

374
00:18:09,630 --> 00:18:13,300
You guys gotta get this kid off my ship.
He's bringing me down.

375
00:18:14,343 --> 00:18:15,177
Scorpia?

376
00:18:15,511 --> 00:18:17,930
